{"word":"κέντρον","slug":"κέντρον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰέντρον, ου, τό</el></b> [<el>ϰεντέω</el> ‘to prick’] ‘<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> a sharp point’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> sting</b> of an animal <b><a href='B:730 9:10'>Rv 9:10</a>;</b> in imagery, applied to death<b> <a href='B:530 15:55'>1 Cor 15:55f</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> goad,</b> used to direct an animal <b><a href='B:510 9:4'>Ac 9:4</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 26:14'>26:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κενόω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:κεντυρίων\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}